It<~>is<~>a<~>characteristic<~>failing<~>of<~>the<~>Germans<~>to<~>look<~>in<~>the<~>clouds<~>*NL*<~>for<~>what<~>lies<~>at<~>their<~>feet<~>.<~>An<~>excellent<~>example<~>of<~>this<~>is<~>furnished<~>*NL*<~>by<~>the<~>treatment<~>which<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>_<~>Natural<~>Right<~>_<~>has<~>received<~>at<~>*NL*<~>the<~>hands<~>of<~>professors<~>of<~>philosophy<~>.<~>When<~>they<~>are<~>called<~>upon<~>*NL*<~>to<~>explain<~>those<~>simple<~>relations<~>of<~>human<~>life<~>which<~>make<~>up<~>the<~>*NL*<~>substance<~>of<~>this<~>right<~>,<~>such<~>as<~>Right<~>and<~>Wrong<~>,<~>Property<~>,<~>State<~>,<~>*NL*<~>Punishment<~>and<~>so<~>on<~>,<~>they<~>have<~>recourse<~>to<~>the<~>most<~>extravagant<~>,<~>*NL*<~>abstract<~>,<~>remote<~>and<~>meaningless<~>conceptions<~>,<~>and<~>out<~>of<~>them<~>build<~>a<~>*NL*<~>Tower<~>of<~>Babel<~>reaching<~>to<~>the<~>clouds<~>,<~>and<~>taking<~>this<~>or<~>that<~>form<~>*NL*<~>according<~>to<~>the<~>special<~>whim<~>of<~>the<~>professor<~>for<~>the<~>time<~>being<~>.<~>The<~>*NL*<~>clearest<~>and<~>simplest<~>relations<~>of<~>life<~>,<~>such<~>as<~>affect<~>us<~>directly<~>,<~>*NL*<~>are<~>thus<~>made<~>quite<~>unintelligible<~>,<~>to<~>the<~>great<~>detriment<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>young<~>people<~>who<~>are<~>educated<~>in<~>such<~>a<~>school<~>.<~>These<~>relations<~>*NL*<~>themselves<~>are<~>perfectly<~>simple<~>and<~>easily<~>understood<~>--<~>as<~>the<~>reader<~>*NL*<~>may<~>convince<~>himself<~>if<~>he<~>will<~>turn<~>to<~>the<~>account<~>which<~>I<~>have<~>given<~>*NL*<~>of<~>them<~>in<~>the<~>_<~>Foundation<~>of<~>Morality<~>_<~>,<~>§<~>17<~>,<~>and<~>in<~>my<~>chief<~>work<~>,<~>*NL*<~>bk<~>.<~>i.<~>,<~>§<~>62<~>.<~>But<~>at<~>the<~>sound<~>of<~>certain<~>words<~>,<~>like<~>Right<~>,<~>Freedom<~>,<~>*NL*<~>the<~>Good<~>,<~>Being<~>--<~>this<~>nugatory<~>infinitive<~>of<~>the<~>cupola<~>--<~>and<~>many<~>*NL*<~>others<~>of<~>the<~>same<~>sort<~>,<~>the<~>German<~>'s<~>head<~>begins<~>to<~>swim<~>,<~>and<~>falling<~>*NL*<~>stra